-- Ford shares drop on GM news pare losses
-- 
-- Fri Nov 7, 2008 12:22pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/11/07/us-ford-stock-sb-idUSTRE4A65HK20081107

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Ford Motor Corp stock dropped 5 percent before quickly paring losses on Friday after competitor General Motors Corp posted a quarterly loss and tumbling revenues. 

 Ford shares were down 2 percent to $1.94, while GM shares slipped 13 percent to $4.18 after falling as much as 16 percent. (Reporting by  Deepa Seetharaman ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )